          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-5">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl" style="background: #8CC640;">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zm10 0a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM4 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2zm10 0a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-navy-800 text-sm">Planning Center App</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-stone-400 mt-0.5">People, groups, giving & more</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/planning-center-tasks/id6751657545" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white transition-opacity duration-200 hover:opacity-80" style="background: #101B2E;">
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.8-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/></svg>
              App Store
            </a>
